lukmanlar a&#351;akdaky synaglary belle&yacute;&auml;rler:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>umumy gan barlagy - demgysma n&auml;saglaryny&#328;
&yacute;arysynda birneme eozinofili&yacute;a &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar (allergi&yacute;a bilen baglany&#351;ykly
le&yacute;kositleri&#328; k&ouml;pelmegi - eozinofiller);</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>gandaky umumy immunoglobulin E - &yacute;okary demgysma
h&auml;si&yacute;etlidir;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>t&uuml;&yacute;k&uuml;rigi&#328; der&#328;ewi - demgysma bilen
anyk alamatlar &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykyp biler: eozinofiller,
&Ccedil;arkot-Le&yacute;den kristallary we K&uuml;r&#351;many&#328; spirallary.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>K&auml;wagt bronhial demgysma
bejergisini&#328; agyrlygyna we netijeliligine baha bermek &uuml;&ccedil;in
&yacute;&ouml;rite synaglar bellenil&yacute;&auml;r: eozinofil kationiki
belogy&#328; we ere&yacute;&auml;n CD23 derejesi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Demgysma seb&auml;p
bol&yacute;an faktorlary takyk kesgitlemek &uuml;&ccedil;in a&yacute;ratyn
allergi&yacute;a synaglary ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Olary allergist &yacute;a-da
allergi&yacute;a &#351;epagat u&yacute;asy alyp bar&yacute;ar:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>allergenler bilen deri synaglary (di&#328;e bronhial demgysma
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik edilende);</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>serumda allergenlere mahsus immunoglobulinleri&#328; derejesini
kesgitlemek;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>allergenler bilen prowokatiw synaglar - burun (buruna
si&#328;diri&#351;), kon&yacute;uktiwal (g&ouml;zlerde), dem almak (dem almak).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Funksi&yacute;a,
radiasi&yacute;a we instrumental diagnostika</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Spirometri&yacute;a, &yacute;&ouml;rite enjam (spirometr) arkaly
dem almagy ulanyp, bronhial demgysma keselini anyklamagy&#328;
usulydyr.&nbsp;Demgysma h&uuml;j&uuml;mleri&#328; arasynda &ouml;z&uuml;ni
g&ouml;rkezme&yacute;&auml;nligi seb&auml;pli, bu usul bronhial demgysma
ilkinji diagnozyna garany&#328;da, keseli&#328; gidi&#351;ind&auml;ki
&uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meleri yzarlamak &uuml;&ccedil;in has amatlydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Demgysma alamatlary &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykanda diagnozy
anyklamak &uuml;&ccedil;in prowokatiw synaglar ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r,
&yacute;&ouml;ne spirometri&yacute;any&#328; g&ouml;rkezijileri adaty
&ccedil;&auml;klerde.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Akokarky akym akymy - ki&ccedil;ijik enjamy&#328; (i&#328;
&yacute;okary akym &ouml;l&ccedil;e&yacute;jisi) &uuml;sti bilen i&#328;
&yacute;okary ekspirator akymyny&#328; tizligini kesgitlemek.&nbsp;Usuly
durmu&#351;a ge&ccedil;irmek &yacute;&ouml;neke&yacute; we &ouml;&yacute;de
n&auml;saglar tarapyndan ulanylyp bilner.&nbsp;Lukman, i&#328; &yacute;okary
akym &ouml;l&ccedil;e&yacute;jisini n&auml;hili ulanmalydygyny we
g&uuml;ndeligi n&auml;dip saklamalydygyny size a&yacute;dyp berer.&nbsp;Netijede,
lukmana bronhial demgysma bejergisini&#328; we g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;iligini&#328;
netijeliligini bahalandyrmaga m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;n grafik
bolar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Gursak rentgen - Lukman demgysma bilen bula&#351;yp
bil&yacute;&auml;n be&yacute;leki &ouml;&yacute;ken kesellerini &yacute;ok
etmek isl&auml;ninde ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Bronhophonografi&yacute;a - 2-7 &yacute;a&#351;ly &ccedil;agalarda
dem aly&#351; meselesini &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykarmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Elektrokardiografi&yacute;a (EKG) - bronhial demgysmany
&yacute;&uuml;rek &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iliginden tapawutlandyrmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in garry hassalarda zerur bolup biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Demgysma gar&#351;y &yacute;eterlik
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik bu keseli bolan adamlara sagdyn adamlar bilen de&#328;
derejede &yacute;a&#351;amaga m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r we bu
bronhial demgysma bejergisini&#328; esasy maksadydyr.&nbsp;Demgysma g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik
etmek alawlary i&#328; az derejede saklamagy a&#328;lad&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Mundan ba&#351;ga-da, her bir
hassa &ouml;zleri &uuml;&ccedil;in a&yacute;ratyn maksatlar go&yacute;up biler:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>i&#328; az mukdarda ne&#351;e seri&#351;desini kabul etmek;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>ne&#351;e seri&#351;delerini&#328; zy&yacute;anly t&auml;sirlerini
a&yacute;yrmak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>tutga&yacute;syz sport o&yacute;namak we &#351;.m.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Demgysma &yacute;aly
h&auml;zirki zaman gurallaryny&#328; ulanylmagy demgysma gar&#351;y
g&ouml;re&#351;de m&ouml;h&uuml;m rol o&yacute;na&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351; &yacute;oly we
gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>N&auml;saglar bronhial
demgysma h&uuml;j&uuml;mine seb&auml;p bol&yacute;an faktorlar: allergenler,
tozan, himiki maddalar bilen aragatna&#351;ykdan ga&ccedil;a
durmalydyrlar.&nbsp;Bu, keseli&#328; g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenmeginden
ga&ccedil;a durmaga we az mukdarda derman seri&#351;deleri bilen ylala&#351;maga
m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Basgan&ccedil;akly
bejeri&#351; shemasy ulanyl&yacute;ar:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>basgan&ccedil;akly shemany&#328; esasy keseli dolandyrmagy&#328;
h&auml;zirki derejesi we alnan bejergini&#328; mukdarydyr;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>bejergini&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik edilmese,
ony “bir &auml;dim &yacute;okarlandyrmaly”;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>kesele azyndan &uuml;&ccedil; a&yacute; gowy
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik edilse, &quot;bir &auml;dim a&#351;ak&quot; (a&#351;ak
d&uuml;&#351;mek) bejergisini&#328; g&ouml;wr&uuml;mini azaltmak
m&uuml;mkindir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>1-nji tapgyra</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Birinji etap demgysma keseli
bilen kesell&auml;nler &uuml;&ccedil;in a&yacute;da iki gezekden az we
g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lendiriji t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;iliksiz.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Demgysma bejergisini bejermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in bellenen kombinasi&yacute;a .beta.2&nbsp;-&nbsp;agonistler we
gysga hereket ed&yacute;&auml;n ipratropium bromid.&nbsp;Tutga&yacute;
zerurlyklary durdy, eger-de, &#946;2&nbsp;bolan&nbsp;gysga wagtla&yacute;yn
hereket agonist.&nbsp;Ativea-da bolmasa, ICS-i&#328; pes dozalary ulanylyp
bilner.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>2-nji tapgyra</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Gerek bolanda &yacute;a-da
kesgitlenen kombinasi&yacute;ada&nbsp;gysga hereket ed&yacute;&auml;n
&#946;2&nbsp;-&nbsp;agonisti&nbsp;ulanmak bilen g&uuml;ndelik ICS-i&#328; pes
dozalaryny ulanmak maslahat beril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Ge&ccedil;irilen
g&ouml;zlegler, pes dozaly ICS bilen bronhial demgysmany&#328; yzygiderli
bejergisini&#328; agyrla&#351;ma we hassahana &yacute;erle&#351;dirilmegi,
&#351;e&yacute;le hem &ouml;l&uuml;m howpuny ep-esli azald&yacute;andygyny
g&ouml;rkezdi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Mundan ba&#351;ga-da, esasy
bejergi h&ouml;km&uuml;nde le&yacute;kotrien reseptorlaryny&#328; (ALTR)
gar&#351;yda&#351;lary ulanyl&yacute;ar, &yacute;&ouml;ne ICS-den has
t&auml;sirli, esasanam g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenmegi&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak &uuml;&ccedil;in.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>3-nji tapgyra</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Bu etapda, ICS-i&#328; pes
dozalaryny&#328; uzak wagtlap i&#351;le&yacute;&auml;n
&#946;2&nbsp;-&nbsp;agonist &yacute;a-da antileukotrien dermany &yacute;a-da
bir derman&nbsp;re&nbsp;iniminde ICS-i&#328; orta dozalary bilen&nbsp;bejermek
bejergisi h&ouml;km&uuml;nde ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Demgysma
h&uuml;j&uuml;mlerinden we alamatlaryndan dynmak &uuml;&ccedil;in gysga hereket
ed&yacute;&auml;n &#946;2&nbsp;-&nbsp;agonist &yacute;a-da ICS +
&#946;2&nbsp;-&nbsp;agonisti&#328;&nbsp;kesgitlenen
kombinasi&yacute;asyny&nbsp;ulanmak&nbsp;hem maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>4-nji tapgyra</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>D&ouml;rd&uuml;nji etapda,
ICS-i&#328; orta dozalary uzak wagtlap i&#351;le&yacute;&auml;n
&#946;2&nbsp;-&nbsp;agonist &yacute;a-da&nbsp;isleg
bo&yacute;un&ccedil;a&nbsp;gysga &#946;2&nbsp;-&nbsp;agonistleri&nbsp;ulanyp,
dem al&yacute;an ICS-leri&#328; &yacute;okary dozalary&nbsp;bilen bilelikde
ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Dowam ed&yacute;&auml;n
bejergi bronhial demgysma &yacute;eterlik derejede g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik edip
bilme&yacute;&auml;n bolsa, h&auml;zirki bejerg&auml; uzak wagtlap hereket
ed&yacute;&auml;n m-antiholinerjik antagonist &yacute;a-da le&yacute;kotrien
reseptor antagonisti go&#351;ul&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>5-nji tapgyra</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>N&auml;sag d&ouml;rd&uuml;nji
&auml;dime la&yacute;yklykda reseptleri doly &yacute;erine &yacute;etirip, dem
aly&#351; tehnikasyna e&yacute;er&yacute;&auml;n bolsa we demgysma alamatlary
aradan a&yacute;rylmasa we &yacute;ygy-&yacute;ygydan &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yksa, lukman diagnozy we birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n keselleri
&yacute;ene bir gezek barlar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Di&#328;e &#351;u
&#351;ertlerde uzak wagtlap hereket ed&yacute;&auml;n m-antiholinergiki
blokla&yacute;jyny &yacute;a-da immunoglobuline E (IgE) / IL5 / IL4 gar&#351;y
monoklonal antikorly dermanlary go&#351;mak bilen ICS-i&#328; &yacute;okary
dozalaryny &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;an bejergini&#328; b&auml;&#351;inji
tapgyryna ge&ccedil;&yacute;&auml;rler. demgysma fenotipinde.&nbsp;K&auml;wagt
ICS-i plan&#351;etlerde &yacute;a-da sanjymlarda almak talap
edil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Keselhana
&yacute;erle&#351;dirilmegi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>I&#328; &yacute;okary
ekspirator akymyny&#328; 25-50% -e &ccedil;enli peselmegi bilen,
&yacute;e&#328;ille&#351;me, demgysma alamatlary seb&auml;pli gijeki
o&yacute;anmalar we gysga hereketli &#946;2&nbsp;-&nbsp;agonisti&#328;
bejergisi &ouml;&yacute;de bejerilip bilner.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Bronhial demgysma
keselini&#328; agyrla&#351;magy &ouml;mre howp sal&yacute;ar we be&yacute;le
hassalar reanimasi&yacute;a b&ouml;l&uuml;mi bolan hassahana
&yacute;erle&#351;dirilmeli.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Kislorod bejergisi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Kislorod bejergisi bronhial
demgysmany&#328; farmakologiki d&auml;l bejergisidir.&nbsp;Maska arkaly
kislorod pes gan kislorod bilen do&yacute;gunlygy (90% -den az) bronhial
demgysma gar&#351;y agyr h&uuml;j&uuml;mlerde n&auml;saglara
beril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Kislorod k&ouml;mek etme&yacute;&auml;n bolsa, bu
demikmegi&#328; &yacute;a-da bronhial demgysmany&#328; (pnewmotoraks,
&ouml;&yacute;ken atelektazy we &#351;.m.) ba&#351;ga seb&auml;plerini&#328;
bardygyny g&ouml;rkezip biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Allergen a&yacute;ratyn
immunoterapi&yacute;a (ASIT)</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Bedeni&#328; belli bir
allergen du&yacute;gurlygyny &yacute;uwa&#351;-&yacute;uwa&#351;dan
&yacute;a&#351;a&yacute;y&#351; &#351;ertleri bilen ownuk dozalara girizmek
arkaly peseldip bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;ASIT usuly &#351;u &yacute;&ouml;relg&auml;
esaslan&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>ASIT doly allergologiki
g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irilenden we bronhial demgysma seb&auml;p bol&yacute;an
allergen tapylandan so&#328; bellenil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu usul, di&#328;e
bronhial demgysma keselini&#328; bejergisi bilen keseli&#328; gowy
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilikde saklanmagy &#351;ertinde di&#328;e orta we orta
bronhial demgysma n&auml;saglary &uuml;&ccedil;in amatlydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>H&auml;zirki wagtda
ASIT-i&#328; iki usuly bar: subkutan (PKIT, bir allergen subkutan sanjym
edil&yacute;&auml;r) we sublingual allergen a&yacute;ratyn
immunoterapi&yacute;a (SLIT, dili&#328; a&#351;agyndaky allergen sanjym
edil&yacute;&auml;r).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Bronhial demgysmany&#328;
hirurgiki bejergisi ulanylma&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Demgysma keselini
&yacute;akyndan dolandyrmak durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini &yacute;okarlandyrmakda
m&ouml;h&uuml;mdir.&nbsp;N&auml;saglar g&uuml;ndeligi &yacute;&ouml;retmeli,
alamatlary we da&#351;arky faktorlar bilen gatna&#351;ygyny yzarlamaly,
ne&#351;e seri&#351;delerini&#328; takyk dozalaryny &yacute;azmaly we wagtynda
kabul etmeli.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Demgysma n&auml;saglarynda
&yacute;a&#351;a&yacute;&#351;y&#328; hiline baha bermek we bejergini&#328;
netijeliligini seljermek &uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;&ouml;rite anketalar AQLQ we
SGRQ i&#351;lenip d&uuml;z&uuml;ldi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>T&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik
faktorlaryny yzygiderli barlamaly - diagnoz go&yacute;landa, bronhial demgysma
bejergisini&#328; ba&#351;ynda we wagtal-wagtal, azyndan 1-2 &yacute;ylda bir
gezek, esasanam &yacute;ygy-&yacute;ygydan agyrla&#351;&yacute;an hassalarda.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Demgysma alamatlaryna gowy
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik edilmese, t&auml;ze alawlary d&ouml;redip biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Astma demgysma, bejerg&auml; jogap berme&yacute;&auml;n bronhial
demgysmany&#328; has uzyn we agyr h&uuml;j&uuml;midir.&nbsp;Ony hassany&#328;
dodaklaryny&#328; we derisini&#328; g&ouml;k re&#328;ki, ha&yacute;ran
galdyryjy &yacute;agda&yacute;y (samsyklygy), ha&yacute;al dem almagy we ha&yacute;al
&yacute;&uuml;rek urmagy bilen tapawutlandyryp bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu
&yacute;agda&yacute; durmu&#351; &uuml;&ccedil;in howply we astmatiki
&yacute;agda&yacute;y bejermek &uuml;&ccedil;in tiz k&ouml;mek
&ccedil;agyry&#351;yny talap ed&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Dem aly&#351; &yacute;ollaryndaky n&auml;sazlyk, gandaky
kislorody&#328; azalmagyny&#328; we k&ouml;m&uuml;rtur&#351;y gazyny&#328;
k&ouml;pelmegini&#328; &#351;ertidir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Atelektaz, bronhy&#328; l&yacute;umkasy mukus bilen
&yacute;apylanda &ouml;&yacute;keni&#328; &yacute;a-da onu&#328; bir
b&ouml;legini&#328; b&ouml;wetlenmegi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>&Ouml;z-&ouml;z&uuml;nden d&ouml;re&yacute;&auml;n pnewmotoraks,
&ouml;&yacute;ken bilen d&ouml;&#351;&uuml;&#328; arasyndaky
gi&#328;i&#351;lige howany&#328; girmegi, lukman&ccedil;ylyk
manipul&yacute;asi&yacute;asy &yacute;a-da &#351;ikesleri bilen baglany&#351;ykly
d&auml;l.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>&Ouml;&yacute;keni&#328; amfizemasy, &ouml;&yacute;keni&#328;
a&#351;a &ccedil;i&#351;&yacute;&auml;n, &yacute;&ouml;ne i&ccedil;ind&auml;ki
duzagy &ccedil;ykaryp bilme&yacute;&auml;n keseldir.&nbsp;Gapyrgany&#328;
kapasasyny&#328; g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;i bir barrele me&#328;ze&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Pnewmoskleroz &ouml;&yacute;keni&#328; berk birle&#351;diriji
dokumasyny&#328; k&ouml;pelmegi.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Entek syrkawlamadyk,
&yacute;&ouml;ne t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik faktorlary (nesil yzarlamak,
gaharlandyryjylar bilen aragatna&#351;yk) bolanlar &uuml;&ccedil;in ilkinji
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351; maksatly we e&yacute;&yacute;&auml;m
syrkawlanlar &uuml;&ccedil;in, &yacute;&ouml;ne kyn&ccedil;ylyklardan
ga&ccedil;a durmak isle&yacute;&auml;n, bronhial demgysma keselini&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak isle&yacute;&auml;nler &uuml;&ccedil;in.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Younga&#351; &ccedil;agalarda
bronhial demgysma howpuny a&#351;akdaky usullar bilen azaltmaga synany&#351;yp
bilersi&#328;iz:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>&ccedil;agany&#328; allergenler, &ouml;&yacute; tozany,
ha&yacute;wan s&uuml;t&uuml;kleri bilen aragatna&#351;ygyny
&ccedil;&auml;klendiri&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>&yacute;elekli &yacute;assyky&#328; &yacute;erine, poliester
ulany&#328;, halylary we &yacute;um&#351;ak o&yacute;unjaklary
a&yacute;yry&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>kwartirany we esasanam &ccedil;agalar bagyny yzygiderli
arassalamak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>arassa howada yzygiderli gezmek, otagy &#351;emallatmak;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>&ccedil;aga bilen &ccedil;ilim &ccedil;ekm&auml;&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>gipoallergen &yacute;uwujy seri&#351;deleri ulany&#328;.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>Howply pudaklarda
i&#351;le&yacute;&auml;n sagdyn ulularda a&#351;akdaky &ccedil;&auml;reler
bronhial demgysma keselini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni alyp biler:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>tozanly i&#351; wagtynda respiratorlary we be&yacute;leki gorag
enjamlaryny ulany&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>Himiki reagentler bilen i&#351;lenende howpsuzlyk
&ccedil;&auml;relerine g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik edi&#328;, dem alma&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>s&uuml;zg&uuml;&ccedil;leri ulany&#328;;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>&ccedil;ilim &ccedil;ekmezlik;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
